messages.text: What’s your address again?
mom, I think I’ve told u 100 times
I know. You know how forgetful I am.
Why what?
y do you need my address again?
I’m going to ship a package.
y r u txting like that?
Like what honey?
honey?? U ok??
I’m confused.
u r just acting weird
How so?
u r txting really proper… u never do that.
forgetting my address again…
calling me honey, also don’t do that
I’m feeling attacked right now.
its just…just out of the ordinary
Here I am trying to be nice and send my daughter a package and instead I get critiqued about how I communicate.
im sorry
I’m just trying to send you cookies and a nice note, from me, your bestfriend.
And you know how forgetful I am!!
but u usually aren’t
Here you go again!
This is what happens when people age. Can’t help it. I can’t be super mom forever.
ok, ok, i’m sorry. I just thought it was weird at first.
No worries babe. Just need the address :)
babe….
nvm… its 1125 N. Luther drive apt. 2
Thanks :) The package should arrive soon…
You’re going to like it so much.
I always like your cookies
Cookies? Oh right, right.
?? whaaa… ok, u r acting weird…
How was your date last night? :)
my date…?
You went on a date didn’t you?
ya, but did I tell you I was going to?
You did! Now it’s you with the faulty memory. Mentioned it the last time we talked.
hmmm.. maybe I did…
Well, how’d it go?
eh??
Eh..? What do you mean?
it was alright
Expand.
well, we went to this bar downtown
And?
it was nice. He bought me food and drinks, we stayed for awhile
Sounds like a good time :)
I bet he was a nice boy.
ya, I guess. He was ok
Just ok? What do you mean?
He was kinda… creepy
What?! How so?
He kept staring…
Well, it was a date honey. Do you want him looking elsewhere. I’m sure you were beautiful :)
…honey…
but no, I get that. He just intently stared at me the entire time, like never broke eye contact at all. Even while we were eating, just stared at me.
Couldn’t keep his eyes off you. So romantic.
no mom. There was this crazed look in his eyes…
Now you’re just being dramatic.
I had to get up to go to the restroom at one point and leave just to catch a break
his eyes followed me to the restroom as well
I think he messed with my phone too
What do you mean?
I came back, I had forgotten my phone, and found it in a different position then when I left it
Are you sure it was in a different position?
I do think so
Why did you have your phone out anyway?
That’s rude to have out on a date.
I wasn’t looking at it
Leann, be respectful next time.
stop taking his side mom!!
boy u r acting strange
Well, did you two do anything else?
we went to play putt putt after
Mini golf? Wow. You always liked doing that! How was that?
I cant believe I went to that too
That bad huh?
it wouldn’t have been if he wasn’t touching me the whole time
He did what?
yeah,  he tried to touch me and get close, disguising it as trying to teach me how to putt
Well, your form is not that good.
regardless, it was excessive mom!
Huh. So you didn’t like him?
lets just say I wouldn’t go on another date with him
at all. I should delete or block his phone from my number
Come on. That’s a bit much.
just as a safety precaution. Cant believe I said yes to this freak
Language Honey!!
oh whatever
wait, I cant find his number
that’s strange
Hi! Miss u:) How was the date???? Want all the juicy details!!!
who is this….?
ha!! You’re funny!!
no really… who is this…
oooo, who is this…. Hehe
But stop playing games. How was the date???
no really, I don’t have your number saved…
I think you should call this boy back.
hold on mom. This number just txted me
You need to call him back and apologize.
wait, y???
For wasting his time.
what the….
Did u delete my number or something??
It’s your mother:)
Huh?????? I’m so confused….
I was just txting u… or who I thought was my mom…
What?? What’re u talking about?
hold on there’s someone knocking at my door.
The package has arrived ;)
r u gonna tell me about the date or not???
hello????
Leann!!
txt me back when you can!!
